{
    "publish_date": "2013-06-05T15:19:23.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT12M47S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "I am sorry I cannot show you my face,", 
            "dur": "3.997", 
            "start": "13.122"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because if I do, the bad guys will come for me.", 
            "dur": "5.086", 
            "start": "17.119"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My journey started 14 years ago.", 
            "dur": "4.088", 
            "start": "22.205"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was a young reporter. I had just come out of college.", 
            "dur": "4.412", 
            "start": "26.293"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then I got a scoop.", 
            "dur": "2.702", 
            "start": "30.705"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The scoop was quite a very simple story.", 
            "dur": "3.419", 
            "start": "33.407"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Police officers were taking bribes", 
            "dur": "2.604", 
            "start": "36.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "from hawkers who were hawking on the streets.", 
            "dur": "3.536", 
            "start": "39.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As a young reporter, I thought that I should do it", 
            "dur": "2.802", 
            "start": "42.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in a different way, so that it has a maximum impact,", 
            "dur": "4.169", 
            "start": "45.768"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "since everybody knew that it was happening,", 
            "dur": "1.888", 
            "start": "49.937"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and yet there was nothing that was keeping it out of the system.", 
            "dur": "3.569", 
            "start": "51.825"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I decided to go there", 
            "dur": "2.235", 
            "start": "55.394"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and act as a seller.", 
            "dur": "3.965", 
            "start": "57.629"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As part of selling, I was able to document", 
            "dur": "3.253", 
            "start": "61.594"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the hard core evidence.", 
            "dur": "2.792", 
            "start": "64.847"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The impact was great.", 
            "dur": "2.522", 
            "start": "67.639"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was fantastic.", 
            "dur": "2.561", 
            "start": "70.161"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This was what many call immersion journalism,", 
            "dur": "3.73", 
            "start": "72.722"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or undercover journalism.", 
            "dur": "2.569", 
            "start": "76.452"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I am an undercover journalist.", 
            "dur": "4.248", 
            "start": "79.021"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My journalism is hinged on three basic principles:", 
            "dur": "4.721", 
            "start": "83.269"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "naming, shaming and jailing.", 
            "dur": "4.8", 
            "start": "87.99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Journalism is about results.", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "92.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s about affecting your community or your society", 
            "dur": "3.739", 
            "start": "94.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the most progressive way.", 
            "dur": "2.637", 
            "start": "98.399"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have worked on this for over 14 years,", 
            "dur": "4.558", 
            "start": "101.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I can tell you, the results are very good.", 
            "dur": "3.232", 
            "start": "105.594"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One story that comes to mind", 
            "dur": "2.231", 
            "start": "108.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in my undercover pieces", 
            "dur": "2.144", 
            "start": "111.057"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is &quot;Spirit Child.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.211", 
            "start": "113.201"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was about children who were born with deformities,", 
            "dur": "4.076", 
            "start": "115.412"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and their parents felt that once they were born", 
            "dur": "2.745", 
            "start": "119.488"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with those deformities,", 
            "dur": "1.689", 
            "start": "122.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they were not good enough to live in the society,", 
            "dur": "2.123", 
            "start": "123.922"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so they were given some concoction to take", 
            "dur": "3.108", 
            "start": "126.045"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and as a result they died.", 
            "dur": "2.577", 
            "start": "129.153"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I built a prosthetic baby,", 
            "dur": "2.817", 
            "start": "131.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I went into the village,", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "134.547"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pretended as though this baby had been born", 
            "dur": "4.148", 
            "start": "136.697"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with a deformity, and here was the guys who do the killing.", 
            "dur": "4.087", 
            "start": "140.845"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They got themselves ready.", 
            "dur": "2.575", 
            "start": "144.932"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In their bids to kill, I got the police on standby,", 
            "dur": "3.586", 
            "start": "147.507"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they came that fateful morning", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "151.093"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to come and kill the child.", 
            "dur": "2.836", 
            "start": "153.633"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I recall how they were seriously boiling the concoction.", 
            "dur": "4.019", 
            "start": "156.469"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They put it on fire. It was boiling hot,", 
            "dur": "2.92", 
            "start": "160.488"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "getting ready to give to the kids.", 
            "dur": "2.472", 
            "start": "163.408"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Whilst this was going on, the police I had alerted,", 
            "dur": "1.975", 
            "start": "165.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they were on standby,", 
            "dur": "2.673", 
            "start": "167.855"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and just as the concoction was ready,", 
            "dur": "3.236", 
            "start": "170.528"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they were about to give it to the kids,", 
            "dur": "3.1", 
            "start": "173.764"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I phoned the police,", 
            "dur": "1.949", 
            "start": "176.864"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and fortunately they came and busted them.", 
            "dur": "4.169", 
            "start": "178.813"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As I speak now, they are before the courts.", 
            "dur": "2.952", 
            "start": "182.982"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Don&#39;t forget the key principles:", 
            "dur": "1.814", 
            "start": "185.934"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "naming, shaming and jailing.", 
            "dur": "2.826", 
            "start": "187.748"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The court process is taking place,", 
            "dur": "2.013", 
            "start": "190.574"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I&#39;m very sure at the end of the day", 
            "dur": "2.083", 
            "start": "192.587"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we will find them, and we will put them", 
            "dur": "2.449", 
            "start": "194.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where they belong too.", 
            "dur": "2.743", 
            "start": "197.119"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Another key story that comes to mind,", 
            "dur": "2.688", 
            "start": "199.862"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which relates to this spirit child phenomenon,", 
            "dur": "4.347", 
            "start": "202.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is &quot;The Spell of the Albinos.&quot;", 
            "dur": "5.476", 
            "start": "206.897"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m sure most of you may have heard, in Tanzania,", 
            "dur": "3.491", 
            "start": "212.373"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "children who are born with albinism", 
            "dur": "2.376", 
            "start": "215.864"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are sometimes considered as being unfit", 
            "dur": "4.053", 
            "start": "218.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to live in society.", 
            "dur": "2.699", 
            "start": "222.293"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Their bodies are chopped up with machetes", 
            "dur": "3.888", 
            "start": "224.992"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and are supposed to be used for some concoctions", 
            "dur": "3.328", 
            "start": "228.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or some potions for people to get money --", 
            "dur": "2.882", 
            "start": "232.208"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or so many, many stories people would tell about it.", 
            "dur": "3.795", 
            "start": "235.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was time to go undercover again.", 
            "dur": "2.556", 
            "start": "238.885"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I went undercover as a man who was interested", 
            "dur": "3.449", 
            "start": "241.441"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in this particular business, of course.", 
            "dur": "2.133", 
            "start": "244.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Again, a prosthetic arm was built.", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "247.023"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For the first time, I filmed on hidden camera", 
            "dur": "3.579", 
            "start": "249.593"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the guys who do this, and they were ready to buy the arm", 
            "dur": "4.744", 
            "start": "253.172"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they were ready to use it to prepare", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "257.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "those potions for people.", 
            "dur": "3.664", 
            "start": "260.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I am glad today the Tanzanian government has taken action,", 
            "dur": "3.576", 
            "start": "263.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but the key issue is that the Tanzanian government", 
            "dur": "3.142", 
            "start": "267.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "could only take action because the evidence was available.", 
            "dur": "4.189", 
            "start": "270.448"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My journalism is about hard core evidence.", 
            "dur": "3.895", 
            "start": "274.637"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If I say you have stolen, I show you the evidence", 
            "dur": "2.399", 
            "start": "278.532"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you have stolen.", 
            "dur": "1.503", 
            "start": "280.931"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I show you how you stole it", 
            "dur": "2.317", 
            "start": "282.434"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and when, or what you used", 
            "dur": "1.72", 
            "start": "284.751"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what you had stolen to do.", 
            "dur": "2.268", 
            "start": "286.471"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What is the essence of journalism if it doesn&#39;t benefit society?", 
            "dur": "4.57", 
            "start": "288.739"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My kind of journalism is a product", 
            "dur": "2.444", 
            "start": "293.309"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of my society.", 
            "dur": "3.417", 
            "start": "295.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I know that sometimes", 
            "dur": "3.178", 
            "start": "299.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "people have their own criticisms", 
            "dur": "3.672", 
            "start": "302.348"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about undercover journalism.", 
            "dur": "3.488", 
            "start": "306.02"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Video) Official: He brought out some money from his pockets", 
            "dur": "4.178", 
            "start": "309.508"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and put it on the table,", 
            "dur": "2.954", 
            "start": "313.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so that we should not be afraid.", 
            "dur": "3.315", 
            "start": "316.64"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He wants to bring the cocoa and send it to Cote d&#39;Ivoire.", 
            "dur": "5.783", 
            "start": "319.955"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So with my hidden intention, I kept quiet.", 
            "dur": "3.688", 
            "start": "325.738"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t utter a word.", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "329.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But my colleagues didn&#39;t know.", 
            "dur": "1.858", 
            "start": "331.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So after collecting the money,", 
            "dur": "3.221", 
            "start": "333.674"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when he left, we were waiting for him to bring the goods.", 
            "dur": "3.128", 
            "start": "336.895"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Immediately after he left, I told my colleagues that", 
            "dur": "3.435", 
            "start": "340.023"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "since I was the leader of the group,", 
            "dur": "1.517", 
            "start": "343.458"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I told my colleagues that if they come,", 
            "dur": "2.997", 
            "start": "344.975"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we will arrest them.", 
            "dur": "1.301", 
            "start": "347.972"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Second official: I don&#39;t even know the place called [unclear].", 
            "dur": "4.227", 
            "start": "349.273"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve never stepped there before.", 
            "dur": "1.584", 
            "start": "353.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I&#39;m surprised.", 
            "dur": "0.967", 
            "start": "355.084"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see a hand counting money just in front of me.", 
            "dur": "5.814", 
            "start": "356.051"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The next moment, you see the money in my hands,", 
            "dur": "3.344", 
            "start": "361.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "counting, whereas I have not come into contact with anybody.", 
            "dur": "3.321", 
            "start": "365.209"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have not done any business with anybody.", 
            "dur": "2.565", 
            "start": "368.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Reporter: When Metro News contacted investigative reporter", 
            "dur": "2.34", 
            "start": "371.095"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anas Aremeyaw Anas for his reaction,", 
            "dur": "2.181", 
            "start": "373.435"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he just smiled and gave this video extract", 
            "dur": "2.874", 
            "start": "375.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he did not use in the documentary recently shown onscreen.", 
            "dur": "4.755", 
            "start": "378.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The officer who earlier denied involvement", 
            "dur": "2.349", 
            "start": "383.245"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pecks a calculator to compute the amount of money", 
            "dur": "3.062", 
            "start": "385.594"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they will charge on the cocoa to be smuggled.", 
            "dur": "4.592", 
            "start": "388.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anas Aremeyaw Anas: This was another story on anticorruption.", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "393.248"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And here was him, denying.", 
            "dur": "1.892", 
            "start": "395.858"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But you see, when you have the hard core evidence,", 
            "dur": "1.961", 
            "start": "397.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you are able to affect society.", 
            "dur": "3.36", 
            "start": "399.711"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sometimes these are some of the headlines that come. (Music)", 
            "dur": "2.307", 
            "start": "403.071"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[I will curse Anas to death]", 
            "dur": "1.766", 
            "start": "405.378"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Anas Lies]", 
            "dur": "2.364", 
            "start": "407.144"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Alarm Blows Over Anas&#39; News for Cash Video]", 
            "dur": "3.357", 
            "start": "409.508"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Agenda Against Top CEPS Officials Exposed]", 
            "dur": "2.853", 
            "start": "412.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Anas Operates with Invisible Powers?]", 
            "dur": "3.202", 
            "start": "415.718"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Gov&#39;t Wobbles Over Anas Video]", 
            "dur": "2.578", 
            "start": "418.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Hunting the Hunter]", 
            "dur": "2.808", 
            "start": "421.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Anas &#39;Bribe&#39; Men in Court]", 
            "dur": "2.735", 
            "start": "424.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[15 Heads Roll Over Anas Tape]", 
            "dur": "4.124", 
            "start": "427.041"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Finance Minister Backs Anas]", 
            "dur": "3.961", 
            "start": "431.165"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[11 Given Queries Over Anas&#39; Story]", 
            "dur": "3.128", 
            "start": "435.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[GJA Stands By Anas]", 
            "dur": "3.387", 
            "start": "438.254"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Prez. Mills Storms Tema Harbour Over Anas Video]", 
            "dur": "3.765", 
            "start": "441.641"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[&quot;Late Prof. John Evans Atta Mills: Former president of Ghana&quot;]", 
            "dur": "3.715", 
            "start": "445.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "John Evans Atta Mills: What Anas says", 
            "dur": "2.177", 
            "start": "449.121"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is not something which is unknown to many of us,", 
            "dur": "3.906", 
            "start": "451.298"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but please, those of you who are agents,", 
            "dur": "4.104", 
            "start": "455.204"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and who are leading the customs officers into temptation,", 
            "dur": "4.583", 
            "start": "459.308"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m telling you, Ghana is not going to say", 
            "dur": "4.353", 
            "start": "463.891"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "any good things to you about this.", 
            "dur": "2.599", 
            "start": "468.244"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "AAA: That was my president.", 
            "dur": "2.343", 
            "start": "470.843"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought that I couldn&#39;t come here", 
            "dur": "2.36", 
            "start": "473.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "without giving you something special.", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "475.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have a piece, and I&#39;m excited that", 
            "dur": "3.491", 
            "start": "478.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m sharing it for the first time with you here.", 
            "dur": "4.082", 
            "start": "481.517"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have been undercover in the prisons.", 
            "dur": "4.106", 
            "start": "485.599"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have been there for a long time.", 
            "dur": "4.186", 
            "start": "489.705"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I can tell you, what I saw is not nice.", 
            "dur": "5.029", 
            "start": "493.891"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But again, I can only affect society", 
            "dur": "2.901", 
            "start": "498.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and affect government if I bring out the hard core evidence.", 
            "dur": "3.576", 
            "start": "501.821"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Many times, the prison authorities have denied", 
            "dur": "3.372", 
            "start": "505.397"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ever having issues of drug abuse,", 
            "dur": "2.548", 
            "start": "508.769"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "issues of sodomy, so many issues they would deny", 
            "dur": "3.98", 
            "start": "511.317"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that it ever happens.", 
            "dur": "1.45", 
            "start": "515.297"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How can you obtain the hard core evidence?", 
            "dur": "3.364", 
            "start": "516.747"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I was in the prison. [&quot;Nsawan Prison&quot;]", 
            "dur": "3.9", 
            "start": "520.111"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, what you are seeing is a pile of dead bodies.", 
            "dur": "4.186", 
            "start": "524.011"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, I happen to have followed one of my inmates,", 
            "dur": "3.07", 
            "start": "528.197"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one of my friends, from his sick bed till death,", 
            "dur": "4.556", 
            "start": "531.267"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I can tell you it was not a nice thing at all.", 
            "dur": "3.641", 
            "start": "535.823"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There were issues of bad food being served", 
            "dur": "3.082", 
            "start": "539.464"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as I recall that some of the food I ate", 
            "dur": "4.91", 
            "start": "542.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is just not good for a human being.", 
            "dur": "4.261", 
            "start": "547.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Toilet facilities: very bad.", 
            "dur": "4.151", 
            "start": "551.717"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, you had to queue to get proper toilets to attend --", 
            "dur": "4.393", 
            "start": "555.868"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that&#39;s what I call proper,", 
            "dur": "2.716", 
            "start": "560.292"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when four of us are on a manhole.", 
            "dur": "3.409", 
            "start": "563.008"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It is something that if you narrate it to somebody,", 
            "dur": "3.74", 
            "start": "566.417"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the person wouldn&#39;t believe it.", 
            "dur": "1.834", 
            "start": "570.157"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The only way that you can let the person believe", 
            "dur": "2.206", 
            "start": "571.991"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is when you show hard core evidence.", 
            "dur": "2.112", 
            "start": "574.197"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Of course, drugs were abundant.", 
            "dur": "3.128", 
            "start": "576.309"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was easier to get cannabis, heroin and cocaine,", 
            "dur": "2.745", 
            "start": "579.437"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "faster even, in the prison than outside the prison.", 
            "dur": "3.703", 
            "start": "582.182"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Evil in the society is an extreme disease.", 
            "dur": "4.711", 
            "start": "585.885"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you have extreme diseases,", 
            "dur": "1.922", 
            "start": "590.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you need to get extreme remedies.", 
            "dur": "2.927", 
            "start": "592.518"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My kind of journalism might not fit in other continents", 
            "dur": "2.734", 
            "start": "595.445"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or other countries,", 
            "dur": "1.682", 
            "start": "598.179"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I can tell you, it works in my part of the continent", 
            "dur": "3.448", 
            "start": "599.861"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of Africa, because usually, when people talk", 
            "dur": "2.208", 
            "start": "603.309"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about corruption, they ask, &quot;Where is the evidence?", 
            "dur": "2.725", 
            "start": "605.517"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Show me the evidence.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.181", 
            "start": "608.242"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I say, &quot;This is the evidence.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.905", 
            "start": "609.423"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that has aided in me putting a lot of people behind bars.", 
            "dur": "4.881", 
            "start": "611.328"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see, we on the continent are able", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "616.209"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to tell the story better because we face the conditions", 
            "dur": "2.584", 
            "start": "619.729"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we see the conditions.", 
            "dur": "2.4", 
            "start": "622.313"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That is why I was particularly excited", 
            "dur": "1.787", 
            "start": "624.713"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when we launched our &quot;Africa Investigates&quot; series", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "626.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where we investigated a lot of African countries.", 
            "dur": "3.201", 
            "start": "628.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As a result of the success of the &quot;Africa Investigates&quot; series,", 
            "dur": "3.651", 
            "start": "632.081"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we are moving on to World Investigates.", 
            "dur": "2.538", 
            "start": "635.732"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "By the end of it, a lot more bad guys", 
            "dur": "2.643", 
            "start": "638.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on our continent will be put behind bars.", 
            "dur": "3.63", 
            "start": "640.913"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This will not stop.", 
            "dur": "1.627", 
            "start": "644.543"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m going to carry on with this kind of journalism,", 
            "dur": "2.927", 
            "start": "646.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because I know that when evil men destroy,", 
            "dur": "3.428", 
            "start": "649.097"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "good men must build and bind.", 
            "dur": "1.988", 
            "start": "652.525"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you very much.", 
            "dur": "1.273", 
            "start": "654.513"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "8.908", 
            "start": "655.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Chris Anderson: Thank you. Thank you.", 
            "dur": "1.698", 
            "start": "665.323"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have some questions for you.", 
            "dur": "2.248", 
            "start": "667.021"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How did you end up in jail? This was just a few weeks ago, I believe, yeah?", 
            "dur": "4.23", 
            "start": "669.269"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "AAA: Sure. You know, undercover is all about", 
            "dur": "2.215", 
            "start": "673.499"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "setting the priorities right, so we got people", 
            "dur": "2.866", 
            "start": "675.714"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to take me to court.", 
            "dur": "1.838", 
            "start": "678.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I went through the very legal process,", 
            "dur": "2.216", 
            "start": "680.418"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because at the end of the day, the prison authorities", 
            "dur": "2.224", 
            "start": "682.634"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "want to check whether indeed you have been there or not,", 
            "dur": "2.616", 
            "start": "684.858"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that&#39;s how I got in there.", 
            "dur": "2.014", 
            "start": "687.474"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CA: So someone sued you in court,", 
            "dur": "1.778", 
            "start": "689.488"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they took you there, and you were in remand custody", 
            "dur": "2.807", 
            "start": "691.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for part of it, and you did that deliberately.", 
            "dur": "2.441", 
            "start": "694.073"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "AAA: Yes, yes.", 
            "dur": "1.691", 
            "start": "696.514"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CA: Talk to me just about fear", 
            "dur": "3.163", 
            "start": "698.205"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and how you manage that,", 
            "dur": "1.809", 
            "start": "701.368"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because you&#39;re regularly putting your life at risk.", 
            "dur": "2.633", 
            "start": "703.177"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How do you do that?", 
            "dur": "1.563", 
            "start": "705.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "AAA: You see, undercover is always a last resort.", 
            "dur": "3.19", 
            "start": "707.373"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Before we go undercover, we follow the rules.", 
            "dur": "2.214", 
            "start": "710.563"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;m only comfortable and I&#39;m purged of fear", 
            "dur": "3.07", 
            "start": "712.777"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "whenever I am sure that all the steps", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "715.847"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have been taken. I don&#39;t do it alone. I have a backup team", 
            "dur": "3.193", 
            "start": "718.327"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who help ensure that the safety and all the systems", 
            "dur": "3.365", 
            "start": "721.535"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are put in place, but you&#39;ve got to take", 
            "dur": "1.945", 
            "start": "724.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "very intelligent decisions whenever they are happening.", 
            "dur": "2.751", 
            "start": "726.845"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you don&#39;t, you will end up losing your life.", 
            "dur": "2.616", 
            "start": "729.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So yes, when the backup systems are put in place,", 
            "dur": "2.504", 
            "start": "732.212"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m okay, I go in. Risky, yes,", 
            "dur": "2.088", 
            "start": "734.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but it&#39;s a hazard of a profession.", 
            "dur": "2.656", 
            "start": "736.804"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, everybody has their hazard.", 
            "dur": "1.553", 
            "start": "739.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And once you say that is yours,", 
            "dur": "1.933", 
            "start": "741.013"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;ve got to take it, as and when it comes.", 
            "dur": "2.308", 
            "start": "742.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CA: Well, you&#39;re an amazing human and you&#39;ve done amazing work", 
            "dur": "2.691", 
            "start": "745.254"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you&#39;ve taught us a story", 
            "dur": "1.27", 
            "start": "747.945"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like no story I think any of us have heard before.", 
            "dur": "3.247", 
            "start": "749.215"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we&#39;re appreciative. We salute you. Thank you so much, Anas.", 
            "dur": "3.844", 
            "start": "752.462"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "AAA: Thank you.", 
            "dur": "1.124", 
            "start": "756.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CA: Thank you. Stay safe. (Applause)", 
            "dur": "4.272", 
            "start": "757.43"
        }
